org.rsna.ctp.stdstages

Class ArchiveImportService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.rsna.ctp.pipeline.AbstractPipelineStage
      • org.rsna.ctp.stdstages.ArchiveImportService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ImportService, PipelineStage

    public class ArchiveImportService
extends AbstractPipelineStage
implements ImportService
    An ImportService that copies files from a directory tree. This is a specialized import service for processing files from a large archive without modifying the archive itself. It checkpoints its progress, allowing the program to stop and start without the import service losing its place. It is designed to walk through the directory tree once. It does not detect changes in the tree which occur in parts of the tree that have already been walked.
